                        <img src="~/images/lt_logo.png" alt="L&T Education Logo">
                        <span>H·ªÜ TH·ªêNG H·ªåC TR·ª∞C TUY·∫æN</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="header-controls">
                    <a href="#" class="lang-select"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i>Vietnamese (VI)</a>
